column1: 4) I am uploading documents on my website. Format conversion for most of them is being completed successfully. However, format for some documents are not getting converted. Why would this be happening?
column2: 4) I am uploading documents on my website. Format conversion for most of them is being completed successfully. However, format for some documents are not getting converted. Why would this be happening?

column1: The documents which are not getting converted might be password protected or copyrighted. So, please check such documents by uploading them at scribd (http://www.scribd.com/) to see if they are getting converted there. Scribd does not allow password protected or copyrighted documents to get converted.
column2: The documents which are not getting converted might be password protected or copyrighted. So, please check such documents by uploading them at scribd (http://www.scribd.com/) to see if they are getting converted there. Event Document getting deleted at Scribd (Event Owner)
This email is sent to a event owner when a document in his event gets deleted at Scribd (This happens very rarely when Scribd's algoritm detects a document to be violating a copyright.).
A document has been deleted in your event.

[header]

A document titled: [document_title_with_link], created in your event: [event_title_with_link], has been deleted at Scribd. The document creator has been notified to edit or delete this document. You may also delete this document by clicking here: [delete_document_link].

[footer]
Event Document getting deleted at Scribd (Creator)

This email is sent to a event document creator when his document gets deleted at Scribd (This happens very rarely when Scribd's algoritm detects a document to be violating a copyright. In this case, the creator may edit the document to upload a new file, or re-upload the old file.).
Your document has been deleted. Please re-upload.

[header]

The document created by you: [document_title_with_link], in this event: [event_title_with_link], has been deleted at Scribd. Please delete this document by clicking here: [delete_document_link], or edit it by clicking here: [edit_document_link], to upload a new file.
